, "rdfs:label":         "Entity reference"
, "rdfs:comment":       "# Value mode: Entity reference\r\n\r\nThe stored field value is a reference to a separate entity.  The selected value is the full content of the referenced entity.  In practice, this is used with render type [Fields of referenced entity](/annalist/c/_annalist_site/d/Enum_render_type/RefMultifield/), with a field group defining one or more fields to be displayed from the referenced entity.\r\n\r\nThe [Field value type](/annalist/c/_annalist_site/d/_field/Field_type/) field should be the type URI of the referenced entity, the [Refer to type](/annalist/c/_annalist_site/d/_field/Field_typeref/) field indicates the internal type identifier of the referenced entity, and the [Refer to field](/annalist/c/_annalist_site/d/_field/Field_fieldref/) field is unspecified or blank."
